The Niger State government has released the names of the abducted pupils and staff members of Government Science College, Kagara, Rafi Local Government Area of the state. SaharaReporters had reported how gunmen suspected to be bandits stormed the school on Wednesday, abducting many students and staff members.  While one student who tried to escape was gunned down, a member of staff luckily broke loose from captivity. See Also






